This directory contains Harness-specific skills that extend Superpowers.
Place custom SKILL.md files here following the Superpowers skill format:
- Each skill in its own subdirectory: skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md
- Frontmatter with name and description fields
- Follows Superpowers skill conventions

Superpowers core skills are located in superpowers/skills/ (git submodule).
